# v3 1000-repo demo tenant is regenerated each publish from the
# leaderboard's frozen scores envelope (see scripts/synthesise_v3_tenant.py
# and .github/workflows/publish.yml). Committing ~2000 per-repo JSON
# files would bloat git history; the publish workflow synthesises them
# fresh into public/ before npm run build.
public/data/tenants/agent-readiness-v3-1000/
